                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Rectangular altar with curved entablature at the top, with carved entabulature for the text. The bottom of the column has broken off, obscuring the bottom lines of text. Additionally, there is wearing on all sides, although otherwise the stone is in good condition.</p>
